# Privacy Policy for Orvita

**Last updated:** June 18, 2026

This Privacy Policy explains how Orvita ("the App") collects, uses, and protects information when you use the App.

## 1. Developer Information

Orvita is developed and operated by an individual developer based in Santo Domingo, Dominican Republic.

Official website:
https://orbita-spin-tap.base44.app

## 2. Information We Collect

Orvita does not require users to create an account and does not directly collect personally identifiable information.

The App may store gameplay information locally on your device, including:

* Current score.
* Best score.
* Basic game settings and preferences.

This information remains on your device and is used solely to improve your gameplay experience.

## 3. Advertising

Orvita displays third-party advertisements.

Advertising partners may automatically collect certain information through their own technologies, including:

* Device identifiers.
* Approximate location based on IP address.
* Advertising identifiers.
* Diagnostic and usage information.

This information is collected and processed according to the privacy policies of the respective advertising providers.

The developer does not directly collect or sell your personal information for advertising purposes.

## 4. Game Center

Orvita may integrate with Apple's Game Center for leaderboards and achievements.

If you choose to use Game Center, Apple may collect and process information according to its own Privacy Policy.

## 5. Children's Privacy

Orvita is intended for users of all ages.

The App does not knowingly collect personal information from children. Any third-party services integrated into the App are expected to comply with applicable child privacy laws and platform requirements.

Parents or guardians who believe that personal information has been improperly collected should contact the relevant third-party service provider.

## 6. Data Storage

Gameplay data such as scores and preferences are stored locally on your device.

If you delete the App, this information may be removed unless backed up by your device or associated platform services.

## 7. Third-Party Services

Orvita may use third-party services including:

* Apple Game Center.
* Advertising providers.
* Apple App Store services.

These services may have their own privacy policies and terms of use.

## 8. Data Security

Reasonable measures are taken to help protect information processed by the App. However, no method of electronic storage or transmission over the Internet can be guaranteed to be completely secure.

## 9. International Users

The App may be accessed from countries other than the Dominican Republic. By using the App, you acknowledge that information processed by third-party services may be transferred and stored in jurisdictions outside your country of residence.

## 10. Changes to This Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time.

Any changes will be posted on the official website, and the updated date at the top of this document will be revised.

## 11. Contact

For information about this Privacy Policy or Orvita, please visit:

https://orbita-spin-tap.base44.app

By using Orvita, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
